A 20-year-old woman was arrested in North Carolina, America,
on Wednesday after a video of her baby seemingly smoking dagga was circulated
on social media.In the 10-second a video an adult is seen placing a
cigarette into the mouth of a baby, The Washington Post reports. The child
shrieks, takes a puff and then blows out smoke. 
Scores of angry Facebook users alerted police about the
